parameters:
\nc<Saki>Is it already evaluation day...\bustMsgExp[1, 2]sigh. I
barely made the quota this time, but it should be okay,
right?

\nc<Senpai>Well... about that. I'm sorry. It seems I've been too hard
on you until now.

\nc<Senpai>From now on, I'll be more careful. You know that I care
about you deeply, right?
\nc<Saki>Huh? Senpai, what do you mean by that...

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Has everyone gathered? You haven't forgotten that today is
evaluation day, have you?

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>No... you haven't forgotten, right? Today will be a historic
day for our company.
\nc<Saki>(Huh... The atmosphere is a bit different today?)

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Heh. Suddenly, I have a message from the president. Meary,
come forward.

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Since your entry into the company on [], and especially
after [], you have always dedicated yourself to our
company...
\nc<Saki>(What? A prank event? I haven't heard anything about this?)

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>...and in recognition of your achievements in nurturing the
best and most excellent employees since joining, you are
granted a vacation of 20 nights and 21 days...

\nc<Saki>(A 20-night, 21-day vacation? What's with this old-fashioned
speech?!)

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Hmm. Remember that it was I who raised you to this point, so
don't forget your gratitude... I mean, make sure you don't
forget.
\nc<Saki>(I really don't understand what's going on...)
\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Now, next... Saki-san, come forward.

\nc<Saki>(What? What's going on with everyone? Could it be a hidden
camera prank?)

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>Since joining the First Demon Industry on January 4th of []
and demonstrating exceptional abilities...

\nc<Saki>...gulp. (I don't really understand what's happening, but I
need to stay composed...)

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>...thus, you are awarded this month's employee of
excellence.

\nc<Demon Tribe Employee>The reward is a two-step promotion. It's a special order
from the president.

\nc<Succubi>The legend of the First Demon Industry! The queen that all
succubi envy!!

\nc<Saki>(I don't quite understand, but it doesn't seem like a
trap... Was my performance really that good this month...?)

\nc<Senpai>Since you have demonstrated superior abilities among us all,
from today on you will be the team leader.

\nc<Saki>Eh, what?! Please don't say such things, Senpai... It's bad
luck...
\nc<Saki>(Huh...? It sounds like an alarm has been going off...)

\nc<Senpai>Please, don't call me senpai. From today on, you're the team
leader who will guide us, so feel free to speak casually.
\nc<Senpai>Of course. By the way, Team Leader...
\nc<Senpai>About your time of arrival at work... is everything okay?
